{"text": " Exhale from the nose, from the chest, from the belly, and empty yourself of air before you inhale. Inhale easily onto your empty body. Exhale from the top, from the chest, pull the belly in to push out the air. Allow your body to inhale easily into internal emptiness. Again, vertical exhalation from the top, from the chest, from the belly. Pull the belly inward and push out the air from the body. On the next exhale down, bring your mind lower into your torso. With exhale, bring your attention towards your abdominal area, with each exhale, bring your mind and connect with the lower abdomen. Towards the area of the belly. Exhale and reach lower towards the darkness of the belly. Reach and connect with the center of gravity. Pull the belly in a little more, push out the air and connect with the center. From thought to the center of gravity. Let go of any breathing, just stay in the center. If thought comes in, exhale from the belly and connect with the center of gravity.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 4.839999999999993, "end": 20.72, "text": " Exhale from the nose, from the chest, from the belly, and empty yourself of air before", "tokens": [50364, 31911, 490, 264, 6690, 11, 490, 264, 7443, 11, 490, 264, 11696, 11, 293, 6707, 1803, 295, 1988, 949, 51400], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.25513483130413556, "compression_ratio": 1.178082191780822, "no_speech_prob": 0.049876704812049866, "words": [{"word": " Exhale", "start": 4.839999999999993, "end": 5.9999999999999964, "probability": 0.5243330001831055}, {"word": " from", "start": 5.9999999999999964, "end": 7.16, "probability": 0.8860094547271729}, {"word": " the", "start": 7.16, "end": 7.36, "probability": 0.9930771589279175}, {"word": " nose,", "start": 7.36, "end": 7.76, "probability": 0.9915246367454529}, {"word": " from", "start": 8.6, "end": 10.52, "probability": 0.9807712435722351}, {"word": " the", "start": 10.52, "end": 10.72, "probability": 0.996468186378479}, {"word": " chest,", 